com.snakybo.torch.object

Class Component

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.snakybo.torch.object.TorchObject
      • com.snakybo.torch.object.Component
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Camera, MeshRenderer

    public abstract class Component
extends TorchObject

    Base class for all components.

    All components on a GameObject are a subclass of this class.

    Since:
    1.0
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
